    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? This beauty is in absolute mint condition and has been my total pride and joy! It\u2019s been pampered, garage-kept, and honestly looks and drives like a dream. You won\u2019t find a single scratch or hiccup here\u2014it's just waiting for a new home! Come take a look, I promise you're going to fall in love with it the second you see it!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
