    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, kept tucked away in the garage, and there isn't a single scratch or dent to be found. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh new-car smell. I\u2019m looking for a buyer who will appreciate just how pristine this beauty is. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
